<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>OAuth2.0 授权服务器</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://cdn.bootcdn.net/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/5.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .welcome-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 100px auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .welcome-title {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #0d6efd;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .welcome-description {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #6c757d;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .feature-list {
      text-align: left;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
    .feature-item {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .action-buttons {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .action-buttons .btn {
      margin: 0 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="welcome-container">
      <h1 class="welcome-title">OAuth2.0 授权服务器</h1>
      <div class="welcome-description">
        基于 NestJS 实现的完整 OAuth2.0 授权服务器，支持多种授权模式。
      </div>
      <div class="feature-list">
        <h3>主要功能：</h3>
        <ul>
          <li class="feature-item">支持授权码模式和密码模式</li>
          <li class="feature-item">完整的用户认证系统</li>
          <li class="feature-item">客户端应用管理</li>
          <li class="feature-item">用户授权管理</li>
          <li class="feature-item">访问令牌和刷新令牌管理</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="action-buttons">
        <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary">登录</a>
        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-outline-primary">注册</a>
        <a href="/api" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">API 文档</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="https://cdn.bootcdn.net/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/5.3.1/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 